1. Reply with your name and I will write something random about you.
2. I will then tell you what song/movie reminds me of you.
3. I will pick a flavor of jello to wrestle with you in.
4. I will say something that only makes sense to you and me.
5. I will tell you my first memory of you.
6. I will tell you what animal you remind me of.
7. I'll then ask you something that I've always wondered about you.
8. If I do this for you, you must post this on your LJ.
Wow I just found out that I was cast as Julius Cesare in Giulio Cesare the Handel opera at CSUN...i'm really shocked right now....WOW!!!!
I have the stomach flu and i'm not happy:(

Hi guys....there is a Northridge Singers concert tomorrow (Saturday 5/7) at the Performing Arts Center at Cal State Northridge! It's gonna be good and i'm sure you'll like it so please come! Its at 8pm and costs $5 with student ID....ok be there..PLEASE:) hehe Love to all!

These made me laugh:)


What's the difference between a soprano and a terrorist?
You can negotiate with a terrorist.

How many sopranos does it take to change a lightbulb?

One. She holds the bulb and the world revolves around her.
Two. One to hold the diet cola and the other to get her accompanist to do  it.
Four. One to change the bulb and three to pull the chair out from under her.

What's the definition of an alto?
A soprano who can sightread.

What's the definition of a male quartet?
Three men and a tenor.
I just found out that I'm working security for the Linda Eder concert on sunday HAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAHAH goodtimes!

-- LA LA LAND --
48. What's your sleeping position: on my tummy with my head on my arm
49. Even in hot weather do you use a blanket: of course
50. Do you snore: no i hum
51. Do you sleepwalk: when i'm sick 
52. Do you talk in your sleep: i have but not as much as my roommate
53. Do you sleep with stuffed animals: nope i don't
55. Do you fall asleep with the TV or radio on: I have to have my fan on. the sound is comforting
56. The Last interesting person you met: Brandon from carousel...my roommate calls him "northern california guy"..he's awesome!

January is going to be CRAZY! I'm working everyday from 11am-4pm and ushering some nights and i have rehearsal about 3 times a week for Northridge Singers and more rehearsals for the LA Phil thing! AND i'm supposed to be on vacation from school??...hmmm!!!!! eh well it is money and i get to sing at the Disney Hall twice! 

Christmas was great! Kir and Geoffy were home and we had a blast...I miss them so much but at least they aren't in Guam anymore! I'm saving up to visit them in Virginia this summer! Well I slept through New Years..Jax and I just wanted to wait for Savi to get home from work..but it was nice to ring in the new year at 2am with a bottle of Champange and Sex in the City!

Well I miss all of you kids and hope someday I shall see you again! Justin (Fluffy), David (Skippy) I miss you guys and It just wasn't the same without you guys here, I love you!!!! Caitin, Paul and Pauly....I miss you guys too you make my day whenever i see you guys..we need to hang out soon and you need to come visit me here ALL OF YOU;) Ok now i must got back to work! Bye now!

Liv




Carousel opens April 7th! BE THERE DARN IT (please;))

I got the part of Nettie in Carousel:) The performances are in April and there are 8 of them so you guys have to see it:)

Life is so good right now! I have 3 jobs and am a full time student AHHHHHHH but I feel all adult-like!!! I met a guy I actually like but he has issues so I don't think it will work out sadly:( Too long of a story to get into right now!
 I LOVE my roommates..they are the most amazing people ever! Savi is 22 and a senior vocal performance major and Jax is 21 and a Junior composition major! So much music going on..it's crazy! I am happy right now..things are nice!  Ohhhhh I am auditioning for Carousel this sunday (for the part of Nettie) wish me luck!!!! Send me good thoughts at 5pm:) heheh
I miss David and Justin I just thought I'd let everyone know! Well I hope everyone is well and I will write more later! Bye guys!

BYE NOW

There is alot going on in my life right now! In about a week I will be moving into my apartment with my two friends Savi and Jackie! I can't wait these girls are great and i'm going to be happy there! Everyone will have to come visit...ALL OF YOU!!!!

In other news...I am performing in Die Fledermaus at CSUN opera and it is going to be a really good show..i have a great cast! The performances are on the 22(fri), 23(sat) and 24 (sun matinee)....i can get people tickets half off with my discount (that will be $10) I would love to have some friends in the audience! I am playing the part of Sally which is the whore of the show..its goodtimes!

Well I miss all of you guys and I hope I everyone is doing well! Love to all! Bye now!

Olivia
